      <title>据称亚洲水泥中国所有者正考虑私有化交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/owner-of-asia-cement-china-is-said-to-consider-take-private-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，亚洲水泥中国控股有限公司的大股东正考虑收购这家香港上市公司，此前这家水泥制造商的股价周二飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/owner-of-asia-cement-china-is-said-to-consider-take-private-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 01:25:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
